      ],
      "description": "<p><strong>Max Ranks</strong>: 5</p><p>A Concussed creature has experienced a traumatic blow causing their mental acuity to momentarily decrease as they find themselves struggling to use complex technique.</p><ul><li><p>A Concussed creature suffers a -1 penalty to all of their Save DCs for each rank it has.</p></li><li><p>A Concussed creature suffers a -1 penalty to all Intelligence based checks, attack rolls and saving throws and checks for each rank it has.</p></li><li><p>A concussed creature cannot gain the benefit of a Rest.</p></li><li><p>A creature can spend its Action if it has a Medicine kit to make a DC 20 Medicine check, ending this condition on a success.</p></li></ul>",
